Prometheus

- an open source monitoring and alerting tool
  - Similar to heapster + grafana setup fro the first K8s course, however can
    do a lot more.
-built at Soundcloud
- Many companies and orgs have adopted it since.
-Is now a stand alone and open source project at the Cloud Native Computing Foundation


- Provides a multi-dimstional data model.
  -- Time series identified by metric name and key/value pair
- Has a flexible query language you can use
- No distributed storage is necessary
- Metric colleciton happens via a pull hodel over HTTP
- Push is also supported using a gateway
- Service Discovery supported
- Web UI (dashboar) with graphing capabilities.
